#: pages/code-cle.php:41
msgid ""
"On utilise une <strong>clé numérique</strong> (ex: 321) qui décale chaque "
"lettre d'un montant différent en cycle. La 1re lettre est décalée de +3, la "
"2e de +2, la 3e de +1, puis on recommence : la 4e de +3, etc. Sans la clé, "
"le message est indéchiffrable!"
msgstr ""
"A <strong>numeric key</strong> (e.g.: 321) is used to shift each "
"letter by a different amount in a cycle. The 1st letter is shifted by +3, "
"the 2nd by +2, the 3rd by +1, then it starts over: the 4th by +3, etc. Without the key, "
"the message is unbreakable!"

#: pages/code-cle.php:43
msgid "Exemple :"
msgstr "Example:"

#: pages/code-cle.php:43
msgid "Message « AKELA VA » avec clé <strong>321</strong>"
msgstr "Message \"AKELA VA\" with key <strong>321</strong>"

#: pages/code-cle.php:45
msgid "Message transmis : <strong>DMFOC WD</strong>"
msgstr "Transmitted message: <strong>DMFOC WD</strong>"

#: pages/code-cle.php:46
msgid "Pour décoder, il faut faire −3, −2, −1 (l'inverse)."
msgstr "To decode, you do −3, −2, −1 (the reverse)."

#: pages/code-cle.php:52
msgid "CLÉ NUMÉRIQUE"
msgstr "NUMERIC KEY"

