msgstr "Result:"

#: pages/code-deux-grilles.php:76
msgid ""
"Les 26 lettres sont réparties dans deux grilles en # (3×3) et un X. Chaque "
"lettre est représentée par la <strong>forme de son compartiment</strong> "
"dans la grille, plus des <strong>points</strong> pour sa position (1er = "
"aucun point, 2e = 1 point, 3e = 2 points)."
msgstr ""
"The 26 letters are distributed across two # grids (3×3) and an X. Each "
"letter is represented by the <strong>shape of its compartment</strong> "
"in the grid, plus <strong>dots</strong> for its position (1st = "
"no dot, 2nd = 1 dot, 3rd = 2 dots)."

#: pages/code-deux-grilles.php:81
msgid "Grille # (sans point)"
msgstr "Grid # (no dot)"

#: pages/code-deux-grilles.php:86
msgid "Grille # (avec point)"
msgstr "Grid # (with dot)"

#: pages/code-deux-grilles.php:91
msgid "Grille X"
msgstr "Grid X"

#: pages/code-deux-grilles.php:102 pages/code-tictactoc.php:98
msgid "Exemple: MIEUX"
msgstr "Example: MIEUX"

#: pages/code-deux-grilles.php:103
msgid ""
"M = grille 2, centre-gauche (avec point) · I = grille 1, bas-droite · E = "
"grille 1, centre-centre · U = grille 2, bas-centre · X = grille X, droite "
"(avec point)"
msgstr ""
"M = grid 2, center-left (with dot) · I = grid 1, bottom-right · E = "
"grid 1, center-center · U = grid 2, bottom-center · X = grid X, right "
"(with dot)"

