"This code is found on every phone. Each key has 3 letters. To "
"encode a letter, you write the <strong>key number</strong> with the "
"<strong>letter position as a superscript</strong>. Example: C is the 3rd "
"letter on key 2, so C = 2<sup>3</sup>."

